original_title: Le Paris Foot Gay: Un seul but à atteindre
overview: A gay amateur soccer team operates in Paris under the name Paris Foot Gay. The club's highest profile supporter from within the profession has been former France national soccer player Vikash Dhorasoo (who is heterosexual) whilst a number of leading French professional clubs have signed their charter against homophobia.
title: Le Paris Foot Gay: Un seul but à atteindre
